        <p>Aarogyam Lifecare Diagnostic and Pathology Centre is a unit of the well-known <strong>Motichand Hospital</strong>, located at Motichand College Campus, Kurmauta, Post-Basdila Pandey, Kasia, Kushinagar, Uttar Pradesh.</p>
        <p>We have been established with a clear mission: to provide accurate, affordable, and timely diagnostic services to the people of Kushinagar and surrounding rural areas, who earlier had to travel far for quality testing.</p>
        <p>Our laboratory is equipped with modern automated analysers and managed by experienced, qualified laboratory technicians. Every test is conducted with precision and care.</p>
